_sText:
I made this map for CSPromod, but i add it in the CSS section to. I added a radar and did some small changes to this version. 

- All textures is implanted in the bsp file. Not the radar files.
- You buy weapons in spawn and pick up some at the ground.

Install instructions:
- Download the map.
- Put the cstrike folder in "Steam\steamapps\your acc\counter-strike source" and overwrite all files!

Hope you like it! : )
